  <body>
  
    <section name="Global maximum bad features test">
  
    <subsection name="Description">
      
    <p>The aim of this global test is to count the number spotd which are rejected by all the unit tests. In this test all rejected spots are counted, not only the removed spots.</p>
    
    </subsection>
    
    <subsection name="Parameters">
    
    <ul>
      <li><b>Maximal threshold of bad spots</b>: The threshold in percent of invalid spots to reject the test.</li>
    </ul>
    
    </subsection>
        
    </section>  
    
